reviewText: The first courses that are part of this specialization are really great. The idea of the project is as well really nice, however I was unlucky to do it in a session in which people were submitting anything, copying the script and this really lowered my experience. The first four modules were really worth it but the project was a disappointment for me.
It's really nice, but it takes months without peers to review and some post incorrect submissions.

A well structured course summarizing the most important advanced grammar points of the three previous ones. To finish the specialization by writing two scripts using the acquired grammar structures and, by use of them, recording two videos was an appropriate completion and a bit of a challenge. Thanks to our teachers for their commitment and expertise!

I'm glad I have reached this final course.  I enjoyed learning and interacting with my classmates.  I wish my classmates would have given each other more support, encouragement, and consideration.  Especially, I appreciate the instructors for creating excellent content to help learners like me.
The lessons are short and fun, yet they are very informative. I have learned a lot of useful rules.

Some of the materials were too simple to understand although some were complicated even for a good English speaker. Anyway, I got a lot of new skills and recommend this course to everyone who'd like to improve English grammar skills or learn something new.
